                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-1">Problem:</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Patients often missed appointments because there was no reminder or follow-up system in place. This led to revenue loss and poor patient flow management.</p>
                        </div>
