                                </li>
                                <li class="list-item">
                                    <span class="list-item-icon">✓</span>
                                    <p>Built automated reminders via SMS & email (24h and 2h before appointments).</p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="list-item">
                                    <span class="list-item-icon">✓</span>
                                    <p>Configured a reactivation sequence for missed appointments (auto call + SMS asking to rebook).</p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="list-item">
                                    <span class="list-item-icon">✓</span>
                                    <p>Created a weekly report dashboard to track no-shows and rescheduled visits.</p>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
