                            <p class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-1">Outcome:</p>
                            <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
                                <li class="list-item">
                                    <span class="list-item-icon">✓</span>
                                    <p>30% reduction in no-shows within the first two months.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="list-item">
                                    <span class="list-item-icon">✓</span>
                                    <p>Increased rebookings and improved patient satisfaction.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="list-item">
                                    <span class="list-item-icon">✓</span>
                                    <p>Gave management clear visibility of patient flow.</p>
